{"tid":2428142,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食壽司郎嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T00:34:10.000Z","uid":351543,"like":9,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7b95e02c9598820f6f516a4a41b521f22b19e18b","tid":2428142,"uid":351543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"話說自從香港開咗壽司郎之後 一直都想去試吓<br />\n<br />\n佐敦黃埔屯門都試過walk in 上網預約個垃圾app 又全部派晒<br />\n<br />\n但我屌你老味每次都派晒飛 啱啱屯門嗰間開幕啲人預早三個鐘去排隊<br />\n<br />\n想講香港人真係奴性重食飯都要排隊助長歪風 仲有啲冚家剷拎啲飛出去買 真係笑撚咗<br />\n<br />\n利申： 究竟幾時先可以食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1d0f6f39fdc65f105c9c2fd8b105766984f98","tid":2428142,"uid":6946,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"11點開門10點半要去到, 你11點先去已經要排成個鐘"},{"pid":"bcc2b70defae11918c66876ec2c8dc4c71d7f08e","tid":2428142,"uid":346081,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"與其話人地在意 不如你睇開d 食第二間吧<br />\n自己食過兩次 質素每況愈下"},{"pid":"44dd1b329f48aff2c5aea366be8bdf7f7969a06b","tid":2428142,"uid":52062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"開舖前9個字排隊通常第一輪入到 （屯門店可能不適用）"},{"pid":"dc1b84ab9c2284de909f8584ef655cd2c79b2ac9","tid":2428142,"uid":160734,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"我唔會嘥時間排隊去食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062a12eb3c373c94651faaef394354fb275a0837","tid":2428142,"uid":388055,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"星期六食完<br />\n<br />\n11:00 開門<br />\n10:35 排<br />\n<br />\n等左13分鐘就入得<br />\n<br />\n肯早去實食到"},{"pid":"c0313c9a0b20d37b56084bf660753cf1a5d3e80f","tid":2428142,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062a12eb3c373c94651faaef394354fb275a0837","tid":2428142,"uid":388055,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"星期六食完<br />\n<br />\n11:00 開門<br />\n10:35 排<br />\n<br />\n等左13分鐘就入得<br />\n<br />\n肯早去實食到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"5d005169b823281b7a882063efbb006bcf48d15d","tid":2428142,"uid":108319,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"樂富最好 D職員夠細粒"},{"pid":"2f20c37c0a38757158930a0d6770b3d928d41736","tid":2428142,"uid":59901,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"Carosell有即日飛買"},{"pid":"8bd6386cf3342f95bf33e6cfd076854cddc87cd4","tid":2428142,"uid":252784,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"惡撚過狗 你想食得 人哋想食又唔得<br />\n俾着冇咁多人 你咪一樣死狗咁拎飛排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e648a8d068f19948e8c76febeb49fbdc43768b","tid":2428142,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係傻西唔早d去攞定飛"},{"pid":"075161b9d6f0f924baa2717bd793214d58a3b597","tid":2428142,"uid":33437,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8bd6386cf3342f95bf33e6cfd076854cddc87cd4","tid":2428142,"uid":252784,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"惡撚過狗 你想食得 人哋想食又唔得<br />\n俾着冇咁多人 你咪一樣死狗咁拎飛排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"同去其他國家旅行一樣，<br />\n<br />\n得自己可以去，<br />\n其他香港人最好唔好出現"},{"pid":"6b7d4c20954f0cce4aaede9141d8552faf7e0b3b","tid":2428142,"uid":329248,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"食過n次<br />\n佐敦 樂富 荔枝角 黃大仙都係大熱多人鋪<br />\n黃埔夜晚有機會少人<br />\n如果想去食 中午 晏就預2個鐘左右排 平日會快d 假期可能要仲耐<br />\n如果想夜晚食 最遲6點拎飛穩陣 太多排隊佢會cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以上youtube睇排到邊<br />\n<br />\n除咗荔枝角都食過 感覺佐敦野食最靚 之後係樂富<br />\n依家有得叫外賣 menu冇堂食咁齊 食過樂富外賣都可以<br />\n<br />\n香港大把食肆要排隊 以前元氣夜晚都要排添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想食咪等 唔想等咪食第2間 冇話一定要做壽司郎奴隸"},{"pid":"78dd5479a20115e567c06592dd03493e12bfd84d","tid":2428142,"uid":198175,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"早幾日去啟田食,&nbsp;早上10點半開門冇人<br />\n<br />\n等到11點過D去到仲有大把位,&nbsp;一條友食到飽先出嚟,&nbsp;超抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b105d249f1d8c725fc600250497ad0c6ebb35f","tid":2428142,"uid":34286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"食過一次<br />\n一般 未必會再食"},{"pid":"89bfa700b3f3ae89bfc122d5f9ad79fb11831a11","tid":2428142,"uid":360975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"食佢不如食立鮨外賣 差唔多價"},{"pid":"6dd58a3ad33a8447c515cc28a0825df1909a1fea","tid":2428142,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"去樂富<br />\n平日十一點零去攞位唔算等好耐"},{"pid":"9655c844aa664b94db4593e4d000ff66655011d3","tid":2428142,"uid":120144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44dd1b329f48aff2c5aea366be8bdf7f7969a06b","tid":2428142,"uid":52062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"開舖前9個字排隊通常第一輪入到 （屯門店可能不適用）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"十點半9x號飛,2點先有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c035408e4bb940c6013b1474b877744a73263c","tid":2428142,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd58a3ad33a8447c515cc28a0825df1909a1fea","tid":2428142,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"去樂富<br />\n平日十一點零去攞位唔算等好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"真,就算晚市都唔洗等1個鐘"},{"pid":"e5e72369b5c104906a0161be37